{"id":941,"parent_id":938,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":941,"title":"Habakkuk 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Hab.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","In his prayer Habakkuk trembles at the majesty of God."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.1","order":"02.36.003.62378"},["b","1"],"A prayer of Habakkuk the prophet upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Shigionoth"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.2","order":"02.36.003.62379"},["b","2"],"O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", I have heard thy speech,",["i","and"],"was afraid: O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", revive thy work in the midst of the years, in the midst of the years make known; in wrath remember mercy."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.3","order":"02.36.003.62380"},["b","3"],"God came from Teman, and the Holy One from mount",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Paran"],". Selah. His glory covered the heavens, and the earth was full of his praise."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.4","order":"02.36.003.62381"},["b","4"],"And",["i","his"],"brightness was as the light;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"he"],"had horns",["i","coming"],"out of his hand: and there",["i","was"],"the hiding of his power."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.5","order":"02.36.003.62382"},["b","5"],"Before him went the pestilence, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"burning coals"],"went forth at his feet."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.6","order":"02.36.003.62383"},["b","6"],"He stood, and measured the earth: he beheld, and drove asunder the nations; and the everlasting mountains were scattered, the perpetual",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"hills"],"did bow: his ways",["i","are"],"everlasting."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.7","order":"02.36.003.62384"},["b","7"],"I saw the tents of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Cushan"],"in affliction:",["i","and"],"the curtains of the land of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Midian"],"did tremble."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.8","order":"02.36.003.62385"},["b","8"],"Was the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"displeased against the rivers?",["i","was"],"thine anger against the rivers?",["i","was"],"thy wrath against the sea, that thou didst ride upon thine horses",["i","and"],"thy chariots of salvation?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.9","order":"02.36.003.62386"},["b","9"],"Thy bow was made quite naked,",["i","according"],"to the oaths of the tribes,",["i","even thy"],"word.",["i","Selah"],". Thou didst cleave the earth with rivers."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.10","order":"02.36.003.62387"},["b","10"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"mountains"],"saw thee,",["i","and"],"they trembled: the overflowing of the water passed by: the deep uttered his voice,",["i","and"],"lifted up his hands on high."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.11","order":"02.36.003.62388"},["b","11"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"sun"],["i","and"],"moon stood still in their habitation: at the light of thine arrows they went,",["i","and"],"at the shining of thy glittering spear."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.12","order":"02.36.003.62389"},["b","12"],"Thou didst march through the land in indignation, thou didst thresh the heathen in anger."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.13","order":"02.36.003.62390"},["b","13"],"Thou wentest forth for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"salvation"],"of thy people,",["i","even"],"for salvation with thine anointed; thou",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"woundedst"],"the head out of the house of the wicked, by discovering the foundation unto the neck.",["i","Selah"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.14","order":"02.36.003.62391"},["b","14"],"Thou didst strike through with his staves the head of his villages: they came out as a whirlwind to scatter me: their rejoicing",["i","was"],"as to devour the poor secretly."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.15","order":"02.36.003.62392"},["b","15"],"Thou didst walk through the sea with thine horses,",["i","through"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"heap"],"of great waters."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.16","order":"02.36.003.62393"},["b","16"],"When I heard, my belly trembled; my lips quivered at the voice: rottenness entered into my bones, and I trembled in myself, that I might rest in the day of trouble: when he cometh up unto the people, he will invade them with his troops."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.17","order":"02.36.003.62394"},["b","17"],"¶Although the fig tree shall not blossom, neither",["i","shall"],"fruit",["i","be"],"in the vines; the labour of the olive shall fail, and the fields shall yield no meat; the flock shall be cut off from the fold, and",["i","there shall be"],"no herd in the stalls:"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.18","order":"02.36.003.62395"},["b","18"],"Yet I will rejoice in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", I will joy in the God of my salvation."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.19","order":"02.36.003.62396"},["b","19"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God",["i","is"],"my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"strength"],", and he will make my feet like hinds’",["i","feet,"],"and he will make me to walk upon mine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"high places"],". To the chief singer on my stringed instruments."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.1a","order":"02.36.003.62397"},["b","1a"],"A type of poetry."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.3a","order":"02.36.003.62399"},["b","3a"],"This alludes to historic occasions when the Lord miraculously delivered the people.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.2.2-3"},"Deut. 33:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.4a","order":"02.36.003.62401"},["b","4a"],["span.small","OR"],"rays of light are at His side."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.5a","order":"02.36.003.62403"},["b","5a"],["span.small","HEB"],"a flame."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.6a","order":"02.36.003.62405"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.31"},"D&C 133:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.7a","order":"02.36.003.62407"},["b","7a"],"Historic allusions as in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.3"},"v. 3"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/3.10.8-10"},"Judg. 3:10 (8–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.7b","order":"02.36.003.62409"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/31.2.1-12"},"Num. 31:2 (1–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.10a","order":"02.36.003.62411"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.18.16-18"},"Ex. 19:18 (16–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.11a","order":"02.36.003.62413"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/10.12.12-13"},"Josh. 10:12 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.15"},"Hel. 12:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.13a","order":"02.36.003.62415"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-prophecies-about"},"TG Jesus Christ, Prophecies about"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"},"Jesus Christ, Redeemer"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-savior"},"Jesus Christ, Savior"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"Remission of Sins"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation"},"Salvation"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.13b","order":"02.36.003.62417"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/68.21"},"Ps. 68:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.15a","order":"02.36.003.62419"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/3.16.14-17"},"Josh. 3:16 (14–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.19a","order":"02.36.003.62421"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/strength"},"TG Strength"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/hab/3.19b","order":"02.36.003.62423"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.13"},"Deut. 32:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/33.29"},"33:29"],"."]]}
